{"title_page": "Destiny (Stratovarius album)", "text_new": "{{Infobox album\n| name       = Destiny\n| type       = studio\n| artist     = [[Stratovarius]]\n| cover      = Destiny (Stratovarius album) cover.jpg\n| alt        =\n| released   = {{Start date|1998|10|5|df=y}}<ref name=finnishcharts>[http://finnishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Stratovarius&titel=Destiny&cat=a \"Stratovarius - Destiny (album)\"]. ''finnishcharts.com''. Hung Medien. Retrieved 2014-11-07.</ref>\n| recorded   = April\u2013July 1998\n| venue      =\n| studio     = [[Finnvox Studios]], [[Helsinki]]\n| genre      = {{hlist|[[Power metal]]|[[neoclassical metal]]|[[progressive metal]]}}\n| length     = {{Duration|m=53|s=43}}<ref>''Destiny'' (CD release \"TT 0040-2\").</ref>\n| label      = [[Noise Records|Noise]]\n| producer   = [[Timo Tolkki]]\n| prev_title = [[Live! Visions of Europe]]\n| prev_year  = 1998\n| next_title = [[The Chosen Ones (Stratovarius album)|The Chosen Ones]]\n| next_year  = 1999\n| misc       = {{Singles\n | name        = Destiny\n | type        = Studio\n | single1     = SOS / No Turning Back / Years Go By\n | single1date = 17 August 1998\n}}\n}}\n{{Album ratings\n| rev1       = [[AllMusic]]\n| rev1score  = {{Rating|3|5}}<ref name=allmusic>[http://www.allmusic.com/album/destiny-mw0000044383 \"Destiny - Stratovarius\"]. ''[[AllMusic]]''. [[Rovi Corporation]]. Retrieved 2014-11-07.</ref>\n}}\n\n'''''Destiny''''' is the seventh studio album by [[power metal]] band [[Stratovarius]], released on 5 October 1998 through [[Noise Records]]. It reached No. 1 on the [[The Official Finnish Charts|Finnish albums chart]] and remained on that chart for 17 weeks.<ref name=finnishcharts/> \"[[S.O.S. (Stratovarius song)|SOS]]\" was released as a single, reaching No. 2 on the Finnish singles chart and remaining on that chart for eleven weeks.<ref name=finnishchartssingle>[http://finnishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Stratovarius&titel=S.O.S.&cat=s \"Stratovarius - S.O.S. (song)\"]. ''finnishcharts.com''. Hung Medien. Retrieved 2014-11-07.</ref>\n\n==Track listing==\n{{Track listing\n| all_music = Timo Tolkki, except where noted\n| title1 = Destiny\n| lyrics1 = [[Timo Tolkki]]\n| length1 = 10:15\n| title2 = [[S.O.S. (Stratovarius song)|SOS]]\n| lyrics2 = Tolkki, [[Timo Kotipelto]]\n| length2 = 4:15\n| title3 = [[S.O.S. (Stratovarius song)|No Turning Back]]\n| lyrics3 = Kotipelto\n| length3 = 4:22\n| title4 = 4000 Rainy Nights\n| lyrics4 = Tolkki\n| length4 = 6:00\n| title5 = Rebel\n| lyrics5 = Tolkki\n| length5 = 4:16\n| title6 = [[S.O.S. (Stratovarius song)|Years Go By]]\n| lyrics6 = Tolkki\n| length6 = 5:14\n| title7 = Playing with Fire\n| lyrics7 = Kotipelto\n| length7 = 4:15\n| title8 = Venus in the Morning\n| lyrics8 = Tolkki\n| length8 = 5:35\n| title9 = Anthem of the World\n| lyrics9 = Tolkki\n| length9 = 9:31\n| total_length = 53:43\n}}\n{{Track listing\n| collapsed = yes\n| headline = European edition bonus track\n| title10 = Cold Winter Nights\n| lyrics10 = Kotipelto\n| length10 = 5:12\n}}\n{{Track listing\n| collapsed = yes\n| headline = Japanese edition bonus track\n| title10 = Dream with Me\n| lyrics10 = Kotipelto\n| note10 = music: Kotipelto\n| length10 = 5:13\n}}\n{{Track listing\n| collapsed = yes\n| headline = United States edition bonus track\n| title10 = [[Blackout (Scorpions album)|Blackout]]\n| lyrics10 = [[Klaus Meine]], [[Herman Rarebell]], Sonja Kittelsen\n| note10 = music: [[Rudolf Schenker]]\n| length10 = 4:08\n}}\n\n==Personnel==\n*[[Timo Kotipelto]] \u2013 vocals\n*[[Timo Tolkki]] \u2013 guitar, [[audio engineer|engineering]], [[record producer]]\n*[[Jens Johansson]] \u2013 keyboards\n*J\u00f6rg Michael \u2013 drums\n*[[Jari Kainulainen]] \u2013 bass guitar\n*Max Savikangas \u2013 [[string section|strings]]\n*[[Eicca Toppinen]] \u2013 strings\n*Sanna Salmenkallio \u2013 strings\n*\"Mr. Unknown\" \u2013 strings\n*[[Cantores minores|Cantores Minores]] \u2013 choir\n*Timo Ojala \u2013 [[conducting]]\n*Mikko Karmila \u2013 